{
  /*
  The connection string specifies a SQL Server LocalDB database. LocalDB is a lightweight version of the SQL Server Express
  Database Engine and is intended for application development, not production use. LocalDB starts on demand and runs in user
  mode, so there's no complex configuration. By default, LocalDB creates .mdf database files in the C:/Users/<user> directory.
  */
